OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777741555
OL,3,CDrug dealer from Aylesbury found
OL,4,Cguilty for distributing cocaine in the
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,FA drug dealer from Aylesbury has been
OL,8,Fsent to jail for distributing cocaine
OL,9,Facross the town.
OL,11,FVasile-Iulian Gramada, 26, was
OL,12,Fsentenced to two years and two months
OL,13,Fin prison.
OL,15,FHe admitted to possession with intent
OL,16,Fto supply cocaine, possession of
OL,17,Fcriminal property, and concealing
OL,18,Fcriminal property.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
