PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777741555
OL,3,CDrug dealer from Aylesbury found
OL,4,Cguilty for distributing cocaine in the
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,FIn January, police officers had pulled
OL,8,Fover Gramada. A search revealed he was
OL,9,Fcarrying cocaine as well as having
OL,10,F#1,795 in cash.
OL,12,FOfficers then found evidence on his
OL,13,Fmobile phone which showed he'd been
OL,14,Fdealing the drug across Aylesbury.
OL,16,FAt court, Vasile-Iulian Gramada was
OL,17,Falso ordered to pay a surcharge and
OL,18,Fthe money, drugs and phones linked to
OL,19,Fhis criminal activity are subject to a
OL,20,Fforfeiture and destruction order.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
