PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777741555
OL,3,CDrug dealer from Aylesbury found
OL,4,Cguilty for distributing cocaine in the
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,FInvestigating officer, PC Levi Fensom
OL,8,Fof the Neighbourhood Disruption Team
OL,9,Fsaid: "We will continue targeting drug
OL,10,Fdealers such as Gramada and taking
OL,11,Fharmful drugs off our streets. Our
OL,12,Factivity will be both visible and
OL,13,Fcovert, aimed at disrupting and
OL,14,Fpursuing offenders involved in the
OL,15,Fsupply of drugs.
OL,17,F"The information we receive from the
OL,18,Fpublic around drug supply offences in
OL,19,FAylesbury plays an important role in
OL,20,Fdeveloping intelligence and supporting
OL,21,Fproactive investigations.
OL,26,@qD@GOUyD@AOU
